'''Ortolan Blue Ferment''' was an [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverage served in the [[NCO Cantina]] on board the [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|Imperial-class Star Destroyer]] [[Steel Talon/Legends|''Steel Talon'']].

It was presumably invented by the [[Ortolan/Legends|Ortolan]] race.

